ON DEVELOPING

00:20:47,546 --> 00:20:49,548
THIS NEW PRODUCT LINE...
YES.

00:20:49,548 --> 00:20:52,585
FROM‐‐FROM SCRATCH, REALLY.

00:20:52,585 --> 00:20:54,253
