THAT ARE DOING $4 BILLION
AND $5 BILLION.

00:21:17,376 --> 00:21:20,246
THE BIG BRANDS THAT WE ALL KNOW
ARE TRYING TO GET SOME BECAUSE

00:21:20,246 --> 00:21:21,781
THEY'RE STUCK ON INVENTORY

00:21:21,781 --> 00:21:25,117
AND THEY HAVE TO OFFLOAD IT.
SO...
WELL, YOU'RE MR. POSITIVE.

00:21:25,117 --> 00:21:28,087
I DON'T BELIEVE THAT THE BRAND
HAS SUFFERED DUE TO THE FACT

00:21:28,087 --> 00:21:29,822
THAT THE COMPANY'S

00:21:29,822 --> 00:21:32,525
NOT HOT ITSELF.
THIS IS JUST THE ENVIRONMENT.

00:21:32,525 --> 00:21:36,061
SO I WOULD HAVE TO SAY
THAT I'M OUT.

00:21:36,061 --> 00:21:38,531
I'M GONNA GIVE YOU
MY THOUGHTS, TOO.

00:21:38,531 --> 00:21:41,634
I DON'T LIKE
HOW MANY DIFFERENT SKEWS

00:21:41,634 --> 00:21:43,803
YOU NEED TO CARRY IN INVENTORY.

00:21:43,803 --> 00:21:46,205
YOU GOT MONTHS,
YOU'VE GOT VARIOUS COLORS.

00:21:46,205 --> 00:21:48,941
YOU'VE GOT SIZES,
YOU GOT THIS, YOU GOT THAT.

00:21:48,941 --> 00:21:51,443
I MEAN, YOU PROBABLY GOT 30
OR 40 DIFFERENT VERSIONS

00:21:51,443 --> 00:21:55,147
OF THIS PRODUCT. THAT‐‐THAT'S
WHERE I'M COMING FROM.
OKAY.

00:21:55,147 --> 00:21:57,483
IT'S‐‐IT'S TOO CONFUSING OF
A BUSINESS FOR ME, SO I‐I'M OUT.

00:21:57,483 --> 00:22:01,187
KIM, THERE'S A LOT OF PREGNANT
WOMEN IN NEW YORK CITY,

00:22:01,187 --> 00:22:02,755
WHERE I LIVE...
MM‐HMM.

00:22:02,755 --> 00:22:04,723
RUNNING AROUND
IN PREGNANCY T‐SHIRTS.
MM‐HMM.

00:22:04,723 --> 00:22:08,294
BUT THEY SIMPLY HAVE A MONTH.
IT DOESN'T SAY "DUE IN."

00:22:08,294 --> 00:22:11,297
AND IN SOME WAYS, JUST SEEING
A "JANUARY" OR "MARCH,"

00:22:11,297 --> 00:22:14,166
FOR ME, FEELS
A LITTLE BIT MORE CLEVER...
MM‐HMM.

00:22:14,166 --> 00:22:17,169
THAN BEING SO LITERATE
AS "DUE IN MARCH."

00:22:17,169 --> 00:22:19,238
YEAH, WELL,
THEY TOOK MY IDEA.

00:22:19,238 --> 00:22:21,240
(chuckles) THEY DID.

00:22:22,775 --> 00:22:26,912
I'M NOT SOLD IN THE VALUE
OF THE "DUE IN" PART OF IT,

00:22:26,912 --> 00:22:28,881
SO I'M OUT.

00:22:28,881 --> 00:22:32,551
YOU KNOW, KIM,
YOU'RE STARTING UPHILL AGAIN.

00:22:32,551 --> 00:22:34,587
I'M NOT SURE I WANT TO BE THERE

00:22:34,587 --> 00:22:37,723
TO, UH, FIGHT THAT BATTLE
WITH YOU. I'M OUT.

