GIVE ME ONE REASON
THAT I SHOULD GIVE YOU $50,000.

00:22:43,863 --> 00:22:48,534
BECAUSE I'VE DONE
$1.4 MILLION IN SALES

00:22:48,534 --> 00:22:51,670
