00:30:21,586 --> 00:30:24,189
I'M AN INVESTOR. I HAVE NOTHING.

00:30:24,189 --> 00:30:26,692
I'VE GOT THE HISTORY,
YOUR MEMORIES,

00:30:26,692 --> 00:30:30,429
I CAN VISIT YOUR GRAVE,
BUT MY MONEY'S DEAD, TOO.

00:30:30,429 --> 00:30:34,132
YOU CAN GET RUN BY THE BUS,
AND WHAT HAPPENS TO YOUR FAMILY?

00:30:34,132 --> 00:30:37,336
MY FAMILY'S GONNA BE HAPPY,
PARTICULARLY MY KIDS.
(Harrington and Barbara laugh)

00:30:37,336 --> 00:30:39,871
AND THEN I HAVE TO BASICALLY
INSURE YOUR LIFE

00:30:39,871 --> 00:30:41,873
FOR THE VALUE OF THE INVESTMENT,

00:30:41,873 --> 00:30:44,576
BECAUSE UNFORTUNATELY,
YOU ARE IT. YOU'RE THE GUY.

00:30:44,576 --> 00:30:47,846
THAT'S ALWAYS THE PROBLEM.
YOU'RE LIKE A PICASSO.
AND LOOK AT PICASSO,
WHERE THEY ARE.

00:30:47,846 --> 00:30:49,815
YEAH, BUT HE'S BETTER DEAD.

00:30:49,815 --> 00:30:53,318
I'M WONDERING,
IF YOU'RE DEAD, IS IT BETTER?
YOU WANT TO KILL ME.

00:30:53,318 --> 00:30:57,622
(chuckles) YOU GUYS
ARE WITNESS, OKAY?
IS THE COLLECTION WORTH MORE
IF ALDO'S ROAD PIZZA?

00:30:57,622 --> 00:31:00,859
(chuckles)

00:31:00,859 --> 00:31:04,196
ALDO, LOVED YOUR PRESENTATION,
BUT WHEN THAT BUS MEETS YOU,

00:31:04,196 --> 00:31:06,965
IT'S GONNA BREAK MY HEART.
I'M OUT.

00:31:06,965 --> 00:31:08,967
OKAY.
ALDO.

00:31:08,967 --> 00:31:11,536
YOU KNOW, I‐I HAVE
A LITTLE KNOWLEDGE IN THIS,

00:31:11,536 --> 00:31:14,539
AND I‐I HAVE TO SAY THIS STUFF
IS BEAUTIFUL,

00:31:14,539 --> 00:31:17,042
BUT AT THE MOMENT,
WE'RE GOING THROUGH A STAGE

00:31:17,042 --> 00:31:19,277
WHERE PEOPLE CAN'T PAY
THEIR MORTGAGES

00:31:19,277 --> 00:31:22,414
AND THEY'RE DEFINITELY NOT
PAYING FOR JEWELRY.

00:31:22,414 --> 00:31:24,483
I WOULD HAVE TO SAY
THAT I'M OUT.

