ALDO, I LOVE YOUR WHOLE LOOK,

00:31:28,687 --> 00:31:30,722
I LOVE THE JEWELRY,

00:31:30,722 --> 00:31:34,092
BUT FOR A LARGE‐SCALE,
MIDDLE AMERICA MARKET,

00:31:34,092 --> 00:31:38,263
I STILL THINK THE PRICE POINT'S
TOO HIGH. I'M OUT.

